* GunStart Field to event GunStart
* Purpose: Resets and assigns the starting gun time for all valid participants (Bib > 0).
* When to use: Run once at the starting gun (after @GunTime or GunTimePrompt).
* How it works: "Initialize Times" clears any previous time values. "Database To Event" then pulls the fresh time from the "GunStart" database field and moves it into the "GunStart" event.

Initialize Times    
Select              Bib
>                   0

Database To Event
Event               GunStart
Time Format         HH:MM:SS.01
Database Field      GunStart